{"tid":1315696,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[喺火炭大圍嘅巴打入] 港鐵緊急事故應變教學　助乘客遇險求生","createTime":"2019-07-14T14:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T14:36:49.000Z","uid":187489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"860c2c852f6aa76bdd60119b6cc495197d9a96c3","tid":1315696,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170216/bkn-20170216083008034-0216_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170216%2Fbkn-20170216083008034-0216_00822_001.html&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP9%2FBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=0157366f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170216/bkn-20170216083008034-0216_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">基哥提醒，在列車內發生緊急情況時，乘客應立即，保持與車長通話，讓車長掌握車廂內情況</span></span>。如有需要，乘客可以打開緊急通風窗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b24d233a4c857a59cf5aa7a060e826f8c27b083","tid":1315696,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:36:49.000Z","msg":"生活小知識 各位記住食早餐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/images/promotion/year_round_caring/banner_600x300_ch.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fimages%2Fpromotion%2Fyear_round_caring%2Fbanner_600x300_ch.jpg&h=856b8689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天氣時常轉變，大家除咗要注意健康，仲要留意室內外嘅溫差呀！<br />\n<br />\n車廂內覺得不適需要幫手？最好的辦法就是在下一站下車，找站員幫你。<br />\n<br />\n健康小貼士:<br />\n<br />\n緊記出門前食早餐，你需要補充足夠熱量以應付行程和緊接忙碌的一天。<br />\n不論任何天氣，都要留意室內外溫差，以免因溫差造成不適。<br />\n如在港鐵車程期間感到不適，盡量找個位置休息，然後於下一站下車，找站員協助。<br />\n互助互讓，請讓座給身體不適或有需要的乘客，並協助他／她於下一站落車，找站員協助。<br />\n大家守望相助，天天開心搭港鐵！"}]}